      "category": "Optional category, e.g., 'VAS' for vessel ideograms",
      "variant_count": "Number of distinct variant forms shown in the tableau",
      "attestations": "List of inscription references where each variant appears (format: SITE INSCRIPTION.POSITION). Parenthesized entries indicate uncertain attribution.",
